img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d6648fca109ca5b50d4fee6c3ca35e85da31da2","tid":1654442,"uid":258793,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:27:22.000Z","msg":"關於禁P牌言, 我想引用返<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1651364/page/49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1651364/page/49</a>  #1214既回覆:<br />\n<br />\n&quot;&quot;一開始話P牌推post帶風向<br />\n然後P牌就唔俾upvote<br />\n而家連回覆都唔俾？<br />\n等到全部P牌禁言<br />\n下次有「風向」，又會怪邊個？<br />\n我所見好多5位數account成日都分化<br />\n同係咪P冇關係<br />\n你地以為警察以前就唔會用連登？<br />\n成30萬會員，得4-5萬係新人<br />\n20幾萬人都帶唔到風向，反而俾P牌帶到&quot;&quot;<br />\n<br />\n禁P牌發言最終只會令係連登傾行動既, <br />\n就返黎黎去去都係個班人, <br />\n冇其他人提供新思維, 咁恐怕連登就只會停濟不前.<br />\n<br />\n利申P牌, 雖然自己好小回PO, <br />\n禁言對自己影響唔大, 但替其他有諗頭/有心既P牌不值."},{"pid":"9cb47a8ef6dad899de8013ea31575a762abb5cfa","tid":1654442,"uid":279236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a5cb394718d81d051b9ff912a297fd596433835","tid":1654442,"uid":302578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c45526fd84a8c9d89d9e7f35719584d39184a72d","tid":1654442,"uid":279236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:25:54.000Z","msg":"p牌同意 只係無得表達我對岳巴既愛慕之情啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:26:10.000Z","msg":"又係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:31:40.000Z","msg":"上少左連登架啦我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢排好攰<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>愛岳巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},{"pid":"35f69c4b0d69df3d762b94ecd8383de0863dfd8a","tid":1654442,"uid":254114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T